= cucumber-in-watir

This project is a drop-in-place project to bootstrap your cucumber integration tests with watir. It provides a good simple starting point to add integration tests to your project with minimal setup.

== Installation

    gem install bunlder
    bundle install

== Running

For Firefox:
    $ cucumber

For other browsers (e.g. chrome):
    $ BROWSER="chrome" cucumber

